data.description: Adorable and affordable one level home in idea location and split open floorplan! Living room has gas fireplace, laminate floors and vaulted ceilings. Spacious eat-in kitchen, screened porch overlooking wooded/fenced yard.  Primary with new carpet, vaulted ceilings, private bathroom with jetted tub, walk in closet.  Large 2 car garage. Recent HVAC.  No HOA. location is close to highways, shopping and dining.
